---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Thoughts on AI, engineering, and building products.
extraCss:
  - /css/blog.css
---

<div class="blog-listing">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="section-title">blog</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 48px;">Thoughts on AI, engineering, and building products.</p>

    <div class="blog-listing-grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <article class="blog-listing-card">
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | dateFormat }}">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</time>
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
        {% if post.data.tags %}
        <div class="tags">
          {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
          <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read more</a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
